Installation may take a while. Be patient. If Media Player goes empty after installation you may need to restart your device. Then you have to wait for indexing to finish, which may take a long time, depending on how large your media collection is.

http://code.google.com/p/extra-decoders-support-for-n900/wiki/Troubleshooting
 
